# Environment Variables Template
# Copy this to .dev.vars and fill in your values

# GitHub OAuth App credentials (for local development)
GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=<your local GitHub OAuth App client ID>
GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET=<your local GitHub OAuth App client secret>

# Cookie encryption key - generate with:
# node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"
COOKIE_ENCRYPTION_KEY=<generate with the command above>

# Your backend API key (e.g., Perplexity, OpenAI, etc.)
# This is set via: npx wrangler secret put YOUR_API_KEY_NAME --name <worker-name>
# See src/index.ts for the exact secret name used
